# ðŸŒ Frontend (Web UI)

This folder will house the source code for BUCCONOMICS' frontend interface.

# Planned Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js / React
- **Styling:** TailwindCSS
- **Wallet integration:** Web3Modal / RainbowKit
- **State management:** Zustand or Redux
- **API Gateway:** GraphQL (optional)

# Features (In Progress)
- User wallet onboarding
- Savings dashboard
- Loan applications
- DAO voting portal
- Community profiles

> Want to help build the UI? See `/contributing/README.md` for our UI design principles and dev setup.
